org.postnote.controller

Class PostNoteRestController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.postnote.controller.PostNoteRestController

  • @RestController
 @SpringApplicationConfiguration(classes=PostNoteApplication.class)
 @CrossOrigin(origins="*")
public class PostNoteRestController
extends Object
    Exposes a REST interface to access the PostNote applicaition (plays a Controller role) to create, retrieve, update or delete PostNote items.
